<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.3">
<l>aṟiyāk kālattuḷḷē yaṭimaikka ṇaṉpuceyvit</l>
<l>taṟiyā māmāyat taṭiyēṉai vaittāyā</l>
<l>laṟiyāmai kuṟaḷāy nilamāvali mūvaṭiyaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṟiyāmai vañcittā yeṉatāvi yuḷkalantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In times out of knowledge you caused me to make love [to you] in servantship</l>
<l>[and] place, me [your servant, in [your] unknowable great illusion indeed,</l>
<l>you who, mingling in my soul, as an unknown dwarf</l>
<l>deceived the ignorance of Māvali, saying “three steps”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
